folder: Watchogue Road & Willowbrook Road, Staten Island, NY
text:
Watchogue Rd., at the S.W. corner of Willowbrook Road, showing the Mersereau House. The house was torn down in 1913. It was the scene of many Revolutionary traditions.

About 1910

By Eugene G. Putnam
